{"tid":1572568,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"小心被跟蹤，反跟蹤","createTime":"2019-09-15T17:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:16.000Z","uid":269871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5931acb7a08892b3901d93e774ba12b88af3d3e9","tid":1572568,"uid":269871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"記者朋友消息：為免前線爆出太多暴力畫面，警方已改變策略改由便衣跟蹤示威者回家途中才作出拘捕。各位發夢朋友，回家多留意下邊有冇人跟住自己，要學懂反跟蹤技術，以保安全。"},{"pid":"068ef676c041ddd735d98bfc492c22b7d5356d8b","tid":1572568,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n[品葱轉載] [文宣戰術] 教你如何宣傳反共，緊貼現在熱門事件。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ebhFbS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ebhFbS</a>"},{"pid":"2a0b2e9253f9cf4ae3adaa634dc97e0aa83ebde6","tid":1572568,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"（重要）大家千祈唔好做以下的事<br />\n1.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捐款支持連登登報慶祝國慶</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fg20celebratemotherbirthday%2F&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDnwORrEXjPgA%2FW0mwV49OOk%3D&h=b0a201ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/g20celebratemotherbirthday/</a><br />\n，不要有錢出錢，不要有力出力（share,推）<br />\n2.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">塗污紙幣，在上面寫口號</span></span></strong>，這是違法的，而且浪費紙張和墨水，不環保，尤其不要塗污港幣和人民幣，這是有辱國體的<br />\n3.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去藍絲商戶集體排隊齋坐借廁所無幫襯</span></span></strong>，這會影響他們生計的<br />\n4.不要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以貼紙來張貼連儂牆</span></span></strong>，因為貼紙既放防水又難撕，這會另藍絲搣到發脾氣兼指甲都披埋，很可憐的<br />\n麻煩大家幫手推<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1572232/page/1</a>"}]}